metadata.name: A Whitewashed World
metadata.description:
As if by magic, the deep blue ocean creates a whitewashed world that is breathtaking and soothing to your soul. The crashing waves bring forth their power in all of its glory and then leave behind this beautiful scene for you or anyone else who may see it up close - within ourselves as well because we become one with nature when faced against such an overpowering force.

A person's perspective on life can change drastically just from being able to view these forces at work before them.
